{"tid":1027891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐冠是c朗面對馬體優勢最大的一項賽事：6戰4勝1平1負","createTime":"2019-02-19T06:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T22:54:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d000d23f777803282943978d0283d91f054d81a","tid":1027891,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"馬競將在本週三晚上迎戰尤文圖斯，同時也是面對他們最大的夢魘之一，C羅。<br />\n<br />\n在職業生涯中，C羅與馬競各項賽事已經交手31次，取得了15勝8平8負的優勢成績，勝率接近50％，一共打進22球，是他&ldquo;最喜歡&rdquo;的球隊之一，只有塞維利亞（27球）和赫塔菲（23球）比馬競在&ccedil;羅面前失球更多。<br />\n<br />\n而&Ccedil;羅的22球，也是現役球員中對馬競進球第二多的球員，第一多是梅西，25球。<br />\n<br />\n梅西在各項賽事中與馬競的戰績只有歐冠略處下風：1勝1平2負，而&Ccedil;羅恰恰相反：歐冠是&Ccedil;羅面對馬競優勢最大的一項賽事：6戰4勝1平1負，勝率達到了66.6％。<br />\n<br />\n而且，C羅在歐冠中與馬競的交手，都是馬競最不堪回首的回憶日期：2014年歐冠決賽2016年歐冠決賽，2017年年歐冠半決賽首回合......"},{"pid":"5e0b6f2fe7f1ed126508a41ee4b5f889a86aa2f7","tid":1027891,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ebedf4cb66122a3491ca54b6ab93d80676c296","tid":1027891,"uid":171107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:02:56.000Z","msg":"贏果4場係隊友carry,唔計<br />\n累球隊和一場輸一場，笑死人咩球玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a1b1b34e8c96f97e15e904c542d49565c48353","tid":1027891,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"馬體要出局了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4b2a7e429a3a380594c91a60cda65e00bd99db","tid":1027891,"uid":25494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:19:46.000Z","msg":"咪燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b2f3f434b5c632da86bcd626c96b9ca0aa7650","tid":1027891,"uid":115150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T22:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h